{
  "name": "Example: Simple Navigator",
  "description": "Demo-level VLN agent assembled entirely from built-in glue (llmCall, textParse, historyLog) + basic_agent encoding nodes (image_analyze, obs_to_text) + the habitat env nodeset. Loop: observe -> caption -> format obs -> LLM decides -> parse action -> step. No method-specific code. Demo-level: shows the loop runs end-to-end; SR numbers are out of scope (see TODO #64 for the loop-body evaluate caveat).",
  "step_budget": 50,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "env_reset",
      "type": "env_habitat__reset",
      "label": "Habitat: Reset",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "seed_obs",
      "type": "env_habitat__observe_egocentric",
      "label": "Habitat: Observe (seed)",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "iter_in",
      "type": "iterIn",
      "label": "Iteration Gate",
      "position": {
        "x": 280,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {
        "version": 3,
        "pairedWith": "iter_out",
        "initPorts": [
          {
            "name": "instruction",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "caption",
      "type": "basic_agent__image_analyze",
      "label": "Vision: Analyze",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": 320
      },
      "config": {
        "temperature": 1.0
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "obs_to_text",
      "type": "basic_agent__obs_to_text",
      "label": "Obs: To Text",
      "position": {
        "x": 840,
        "y": 320
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "planner_llm",
      "type": "llmCall",
      "label": "LLM: Decide Action",
      "position": {
        "x": 1120,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {
        "ports": [
          {
            "name": "instruction",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "observation",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "history",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "required": false
          }
        ],
        "template": "Instruction: {instruction}\n\nCurrent observation:\n{observation}\n\nAction history:\n{history}\n\nChoose exactly one action: FORWARD (move 0.25m ahead), LEFT (turn 15 degrees), RIGHT (turn 15 degrees), or STOP (only when you believe you have reached the goal). Give one short sentence of reasoning, then write the action keyword alone on the last line.",
        "system_prompt": "You are a navigation agent inside an indoor environment. You follow the instruction step by step.",
        "profile": "",
        "temperature": 1.0,
        "max_tokens": 2000,
        "mode": "single_turn"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "parse_action",
      "type": "textParse",
      "label": "Parse Action",
      "position": {
        "x": 1400,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {
        "mode": "choice",
        "choices": "STOP,FORWARD,LEFT,RIGHT",
        "scan": "last_line_first",
        "default": "FORWARD"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "history_log",
      "type": "historyLog",
      "label": "History Log",
      "position": {
        "x": 1680,
        "y": 380
      },
      "config": {
        "max_entries": 20,
        "template": "Step {step}: {entry}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "env_step",
      "type": "env_habitat__step_discrete",
      "label": "Habitat: Step",
      "position": {
        "x": 1680,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "loop_obs",
      "type": "env_habitat__observe_egocentric",
      "label": "Habitat: Observe (loop)",
      "position": {
        "x": 1960,
        "y": 320
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "iter_out",
      "type": "iterOut",
      "label": "Iteration End",
      "position": {
        "x": 2240,
        "y": 200
      },
      "config": {
        "pairedWith": "iter_in",
        "ports": [
          {
            "name": "rgb",
            "wire_type": "IMAGE",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "pose",
            "wire_type": "POSE",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "history",
            "wire_type": "TEXT",
            "persist": true,
            "required": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "evaluate",
      "type": "env_habitat__evaluate",
      "label": "Habitat: Evaluate",
      "position": {
        "x": 1960,
        "y": 500
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "obs_viewer",
      "type": "imageViewer",
      "label": "Observation",
      "position": {
        "x": 2240,
        "y": 560
      },
      "config": {
        "rows": 1,
        "cols": 1,
        "ports": [
          {
            "name": "rgb",
            "wire_type": "IMAGE"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "reasoning_scroll",
      "type": "textScroll",
      "label": "LLM Reasoning",
      "position": {
        "x": 1120,
        "y": 560
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "action_log_viewer",
      "type": "actionLog",
      "label": "Action Log",
      "position": {
        "x": 1400,
        "y": 560
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "metrics_viewer",
      "type": "metrics",
      "label": "Metrics",
      "position": {
        "x": 1960,
        "y": 660
      },
      "config": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "output_port__metrics",
      "type": "graphOut",
      "label": "metrics",
      "position": {
        "x": 2240,
        "y": 700
      },
      "config": {
        "portName": "metrics",
        "wireType": "METRICS"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "note_demo",
      "type": "note",
      "label": "Demo: built-in navigator",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": -260
      },
      "config": {
        "markdown": "**Demo: a navigator from built-in parts only**\n\nEvery reasoning node here ships with the platform:\n\n- `llmCall` (built-in) — prompt template + LLM call\n- `textParse` (built-in) — choice mode; index 0-3 doubles as the discrete env action\n- `historyLog` (built-in) — per-step history, loop-carried via iterOut\n- `basic_agent__image_analyze` + `obs_to_text` (standard nodeset) — observation encoding\n\nThe env side is the habitat nodeset's gym verbs (reset / observe / step / evaluate). No method-specific code anywhere.\n\n*Demo-level*: shows the loop runs; headline SR is out of scope (loop-body evaluate misses the terminal STOP step — TODO #64)."
      }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "id": "e_reset_instruction_to_init",
      "source": "env_reset",
      "target": "iter_in",
      "sourceHandle": "instruction",
      "targetHandle": "init_instruction"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_reset_to_seedobs",
      "source": "env_reset",
      "target": "seed_obs",
      "sourceHandle": "episode_id",
      "targetHandle": "trigger"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_seedobs_rgb_to_iterin",
      "source": "seed_obs",
      "target": "iter_in",
      "sourceHandle": "rgb",
      "targetHandle": "iterout_rgb"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_seedobs_pose_to_iterin",
      "source": "seed_obs",
      "target": "iter_in",
      "sourceHandle": "pose",
      "targetHandle": "iterout_pose"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iterin_rgb_to_caption",
      "source": "iter_in",
      "target": "caption",
      "sourceHandle": "iterout_rgb",
      "targetHandle": "image"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_caption_to_obstext",
      "source": "caption",
      "target": "obs_to_text",
      "sourceHandle": "response",
      "targetHandle": "caption"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iterin_pose_to_obstext",
      "source": "iter_in",
      "target": "obs_to_text",
      "sourceHandle": "iterout_pose",
      "targetHandle": "pose"
    },
    {
      "id": "e_iterin_instruction_to_llm",
